    "description": "Parent app APIs under `/api/v1/parent`. **CRITICAL:** Set `base_url` to `https://YOUR-HOST/api/v1` (must end with `/api/v1`). If you omit `/api/v1`, URLs become `.../parent/...` and the server returns 404 NOT_FOUND. Source: `backend/src/modules/parent/parent.routes.js`. Run **01 Auth → POST /auth/login (PARENT user)** first."
  },
